                                    <hr class="WUdCTb"/>
                                    <h2 class=" Igsabe">
                                        <span class="lead__title-content" data-field="summary-header">What can I notarize for you today?</span>
                                    </h2>
                                    <div class="lead__summary-content" data-field="summary-body" jslog="61736; track:impression" jsname="U0N86e" itemprop="disambiguatingDescription">
                                        <div>My name is Melani and I own and operate Branch Mobile Notary where I provide my notary services with a professional, yet charismatic approach.
 </div>
                                        <div>
                                            <br>
                                        </div>
                                        <div>As a Notary Public, I am an official of integrity commissioned by the Missouri Secretary of State, authorized to impartially witness and validate signatures on a wide variety of documents. </div>
                                        <div>
                                            <br>
                                        </div>
                                        <div>
                                            I am a mobile service which means I come to you, saving you time and at your convenience. <br>
                                        </div>
                                        <div>
                                            <br>
                                        </div>
                                        <div>
                                            I am not an attorney so I cannot offer any legal advice. <br>
                                        </div>
                                        <div>
                                            <br>
                                        </div>
                                        <div>Please reach out if can be of service.</div>
